<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="UTF-8"><style>body{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;color:#333}.container{max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px}.header{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ef4444 0%,#dc2626 100%);color:white;padding:30px;text-align:center;border-radius:8px 8px 0 0}.content{background:#fff;padding:30px;border:1px solid #e5e7eb}.success{text-align:center;font-size:48px;color:#10b981}.info-box{background:#fef2f2;border-left:4px solid #ef4444;padding:15px;margin:20px 0}.button{display:inline-block;padding:12px 30px;background:#ef4444;color:white;text-decoration:none;border-radius:5px}.footer{background:#f9fafb;padding:20px;text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:#6b7280}</style></head>
<body><div class="container"><div class="header"><h1>⚠️ Challenge Report Submitted</h1></div><div class="content"><div class="success">✓</div><h2 style="text-align:center;color:#10b981;">Report Submitted</h2><p>Dear {{ $report->user->name }},</p><p>Your challenge report "<strong>{{ $report->title }}</strong>" has been submitted.</p><div class="info-box"><strong>Type:</strong> {{ ucfirst(str_replace('_', ' ', $report->challenge_type)) }}<br><strong>Severity:</strong> {{ ucfirst($report->severity) }}<br><strong>Status:</strong> {{ ucfirst($report->status) }}<br><strong>Submitted:</strong> {{ $report->created_at->format('F d, Y') }}</div><p>We take all challenges seriously and our support team will reach out to you soon.</p><div style="text-align:center"><a href="{{ url('/scholar/challenges/my-challenges') }}" class="button">View My Reports</a></div><p>You're not alone in this.<br><strong>The OA Foundation Team</strong></p></div><div class="footer"><p>&copy; {{ date('Y') }} OA Foundation</p></div></div></body></html>
